item.title: some ideas.
item.description: Today was cool. I thought up a bunch of interesting ideas. and that was all. jesus. i am tired. i can’t pay attention for the life of me. its killing me. i am watching Entourage. back a couple days ago i went to an Entourage opening party at crobar. i rode my bike. it was right after i got my bike and had fixed it all up. i had rode it to juggling club then after that swung over to crobar to check out this party.
